data.description: Nestled in a beautiful well-manicured subdivision with only 20 homes. This Fabulous 4-sided brick home is perfect for entertaining. This beauty is move-in ready and features a formal dining and living room, a spacious great room with coffered ceilings and a stunning brick fireplace. There is also a huge owner suite with double tray ceilings, and a large sitting room. Let’s explore the outdoor amenities....Save time, conserve water, and increase curb appeal with the previously installed irrigation system. Get your daily source of fiber as well as antioxidants from the 2 plum trees located in the backyard. Not only is this beauty spacious it has an abundance of storage. Check out the 10x10 storage unit outside. There is also an incredible Ramadas used for BBQing. You definitely won’t be disappointed!!! Schedule a tour today 404-271-6227!!!  NO HOA!!
